These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  teacher, lawyer, journalist, engineer, writer, firefighter, architect
There are 7 different nationalities: british, indonesian, egyptian, german, spanish, pakistani, turkish
 1. the engineer is on the left of the german##1
 2. the spanish is the engineer##1
 3. the architect is on the right of the firefighter##1
 4. the egyptian is on the right of the pakistani##1
 5. the journalist is in the middle##1
 6. the british is on the far left##1
 7. the writer is the british##1
 8. the teacher is on the right of the pakistani##1
 9. the egyptian is on the left of the indonesian##1
10. the german is on the left of the journalist##1
11. the architect is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | writer | engineer | lawyer | journalist | teacher | firefighter | architect |
| Nationality   | british    | spanish   | german      | pakistani | egyptian    | indonesian    | turkish         |

