.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cherry, tomato, pear, pumpkin, avocado, cauliflower, blueberry
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, techno, r&b, trance, country, jazz, disco
 1. the fan of country is the person eating pumpkin##1
 2. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 3. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating tomato is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the fan of country is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating pear##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cherry | tomato | avocado | pumpkin | cauliflower | blueberry | pear |
| Music-Genre   | techno      | r&b   | trance   | country      | folk       | disco       | jazz     |

