.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: eggplant, orange, kale, pumpkin, plum, cherry, carrot
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, coach, nurse, security-guard, chef, librarian, videographer
 1. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 2. the person eating plum is on the left of the videographer##1
 3. the coach is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the architect is the person eating plum##1
 6. the nurse is on the right of the coach##1
 7. the coach is on the left of the nurse##1
 8. the coach is on the right of the security-guard##1
 9. the person eating cherry is the security-guard##1
10. the person eating kale is on the right of the architect##1
11. the security-guard is in the middle##1
12. the person eating carrot is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | orange | plum     | kale  | cherry       | eggplant       | carrot  | pumpkin   |
| Job    | librarian  | architect | videographer | security-guard | coach | nurse | chef |

