.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, funk, dubstep, pop, ambient, techno
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, japanese, american, pakistani, italian, canadian
 1. the fan of pop is the turkish##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 3. the italian is on the right of the japanese##1
 4. the malaysian is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 5. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
 7. the japanese is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the right of the italian##1
 9. the fan of funk is the pakistani##1
10. the pakistani is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
11. the canadian is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | techno     | dubstep     | funk      | hip-hop | pop      | blues     |
| Nationality   | american | japanese | italian | pakistani | canadian | turkish | malaysian |

