.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: chess, skydiving, filmmaking, puzzles, singing, writing, ferreting
7 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, rabbit, hamster, turtle, lizard, hedgehog
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is ferreting##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is ferreting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | skydiving | filmmaking | writing     | puzzles | ferreting | singing | chess |
| Pet     | hedgehog   | rabbit    | turtle | lizard     | rat         | hamster     | ferret        |

