.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, water, mirinda, cola, tea, milk
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, van, roller, car, boat, subway
 1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | water | tea   | lemonade | mirinda | milk  | cola | hot-chocolate |
| Transport   | roller   | car | snowmobile | boat     | motorbike | subway | van   |

