.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy, mystery, epic, disaster, horror, sports
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, subway, taxi, car, ship, tram
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the taxi##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | sports | epic | disaster | horror     | comedy | mystery |
| Transport     | ship | taxi      | tram | subway    | car | helicopter   | airplane  |

