 4. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby       | collecting   | board-games | magic-tricks | sudoku | camping     | traveling | photography |
| Transport   | ship | snowmobile      | skateboard        | van         | tram | bus     | bike |

